{"title":"我等待你，同努力！——寄给我在第四野战军作战的爱人","authors":["汪以引"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":5,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"我等待你，同努力！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——寄给我在第四野战军作战的爱人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汪以引"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你走了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带着对人民强烈的爱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带着对革命忠实的热情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留不住你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不想留住你。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们争过的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了人民的明天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你一定要走上前线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我一定要在后方建设，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁也不让谁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你走了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我留下来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都要坚持自己的责任。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你走了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"剩下我在矛盾；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我也想去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想跟着你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但，这是懦怯，是自私。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你走了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身旁少了你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"课堂里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"饭厅里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"失去了关注我的眼睛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我不曾一刻忘记过你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这想念——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是我紧张生活的动力。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今夜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更想你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"武汉解放了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光荣的胜利里也夹了一份你的功绩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我骄傲！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我兴奋！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我仿佛看见："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你争坐渡江的第一只船，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你第一个翻过敌人炮火集中的山岭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你永远勇往争先，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你经得起考验，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我不会错误估价你。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勇敢地战斗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早胜利归来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更艰苦的工作需要我们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我等待你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同努力！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}